name: Newly Webbed
description:
Controlls:

Player 1: W, A, D

Player 2: Arrow keys

In Newley Webbs this co-op platformer you play as a one of the spiders that has to reach to the rooftop to get back to there wedding after falling down straight to the basement. So you and a friend must climb back up to the rooftop so they can live happily ever after.

Artist: Andrew Day 

Programmers: Jackson Holliman and Josh Mcmillin

Sound/Music : Christian Ekpenike

Programs used:

Unity

Grojband

Audacity

Krita

Clip Studio

Hint: keep trying to go up at the end PLZ!
